description:
Product description

MONO VALVE, RIGHT SIDE
EXPANDABLE - MILITARY

TECLINE MILITARY
Tecline products designed to meet the specifications of Armies and Special Forces.
Availability of Tecline Military products depends on manufacturing surpluses.

Expandable single valve allows to dive with a single cylinder or in a sidemount configuration.
Due to its design, this valve can be used as part of a manifold in a twinset configuration.

SPECIFICATIONS:
- Expandable single valve (right)
- Working pressure: 300 bar
- Material: maritime bronze with double coating (chrome + PVD*)
- Thread for scuba regulator connection: DIN G5/8
- Thread for cylinder: M25/2
- Cylinger connection o-ring included
- Siphon to prevent moisture accumulation in the valve
- Rubber knob

*PVD - (Physical Vapor Deposition) is a variety of methods used to produce extremely thin and resistant coatings.

APPLICATION:
-single cylinders
-double sets
-sidemount
